replies.body:
This may be caused by hardware issues or driver problems, as they're common causes for system freezes. I recommend first ensuring this isn't caused by the Xbox Game Bar (if you're running Windows 10) by [disabling the game bar entirely. ](http://www.tenforums.com/tutorials/8637-game-bar-turn-off-windows-10-a.html) If you continue to have issues, I recommend working through the steps in our [Bugsplat & Crash guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201761974-Bug-Splat-and-Game-Crashes)

Let me know if those steps caused any change in your freezing.
